Webex App | Update Your Display Name
You can change your display name for your Webex App profile to your preferred name. For example, if your name is Jennifer, but most people know you as Jen.
Desktop
iPhone and iPad
Android
Web
1
In the app header, click your profile picture.
2
Click Edit profile, then go to the Display name section.
3
Click on your name, and make your changes.

  If you can't change your name, check with your support department because they've likely set it that way on purpose.
4
Then, click Save.